OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy on Saturday,
OL,6,Fthough a few sunny spells likely
OL,7,Fdeveloping across the east of the
OL,8,Fregion. Many places dry, but risk of
OL,9,Fsome rain or showers at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMore
OL,12,Funsettled than recently, with rain or
OL,13,Fshowers, some thundery. Gradually
OL,14,Fturning cooler. More sunny spells from
OL,15,FMonday, but still also showers, these
OL,16,Fbecoming lighter and further between
OL,17,Fon Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
